\v 4 Kabayikuthululela\x + \xt Hos. 3.4.\x* iwayini eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, kabayikuyithokozisa\x + \xt Jer. 6.20; Hos. 8.13.\x*; imihlatshelo yabo izakuba njengesinkwa\x + \xt Dute. 26.14; Jer. 16.7; Hez. 24.17.\x* sokulila kubo; bonke\x + \xt Nani 19.14; Hagg. 2.13.\x* abasidlayo bazangcola; ngoba isinkwa sabo ngesomphefumulo wabo, kasiyikufika endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 5 Lizakwenzani ngosuku lomkhosi\x + \xt Hos. 2.11.\x* omisiweyo, langosuku lwedili\x + \xt Hos. 2.11.\x* leN\nd kosi\nd*?
\v 6 Ngoba khangela, bahambile ngenxa yokuchitheka\x + \xt Hos. 7.13.\x*, iGibhithe\x + \xt Hos. 8.13; 11.5,6; 7.16; Jer. 44.11-27.\x* izababutha, iMofi\x + \xt Isa. 19.13.\x* ibangcwabe, \add izindawo\add* zabo eziloyisekayo\x + \xt 1 Kho. 20.6; Hez. 24.16,21,25,16. Jow. 3.5.\x* zesiliva, ukhula oluhlabayo\x + \xt Isa. 34.13; Isa. 32.13; 10.8.\x* luzakudla ilifa lazo, ameva\x + \xt Isa. 34.13; Isa. 32.13; 10.8.\x* abe semathenteni abo.
