\v 7 Insuku\x + \xt Isa. 10.3.\x* zokuhanjelwa sezifikile, insuku zempindiselo\x + \xt Jobe 21.19.\x* sezifikile; uIsrayeli\x + \xt Jobe 21.19.\x* uzakwazi; umprofethi\x + \xt Hez. 13.3; Zef. 3.4.\x* uyisithutha, umuntu womoya\x + \xt Hez. 13.3; Zef. 3.4.\x*\x + \xt Mika 2.11.\x* uyahlanya\x + \xt Dute. 28.34; 2 Kho. 9.11.\x*, ngenxa yobunengi bobubi benu, lenzondo enkulu.
