\v 9 Ba\add z\add*onakalisile\x + \xt Dute. 31.29.\x* ngokujulileyo\x + \xt Hos. 5.2.\x* njengensukwini\x + \xt Hlu. 19.22; Hos. 10.9; 5.8.\x* zeGibeya. Uzakhumbula\x + \xt Hos. 8.13.\x* ububi babo, ajezise\x + \xt Hos. 8.13.\x* izono zabo.
\v 10 Ngamthola uIsrayeli njengezithelo zevini enkangala, ngababona oyihlo njengezithelo\x + \xt Isa. 28.4; Mika 7.1; Nah. 3.12; Jer. 24.2.\x* zokuqala\x + \xt Hos. 2.15.\x* emkhiweni ekuqaleni kwazo. \add Kodwa\add* bona\x + \xt Nani 25.3; Hlab. 106.28.\x* baya eBhali-Peyori\x + \xt Nani 23.28.\x*, bazehlukanisela\x + \xt Hos. 4.14.\x* lelohlazo\x + \xt Jer. 11.13.\x*, baba\x + \xt Amos 4.5; Hlab. 81.12.\x* ngokunengekayo njengokuthanda kwabo.
\v 11 \add Ngo\add*Efrayimi, udumo lwabo\x + \xt Hos. 10.5.\x* luzaphapha luhambe njengenyoni, kusukela ekuzalweni, njalo kusukela\x + \xt Hos. 9.16.\x* esiswini, njalo kusukela ekumithweni.
\v 12 Loba\x + \xt Jobe 27.14; Lilo 2.22,16; Hos. 13.16; Isa. 65.23.\x* bekhulisa abantwana babo, kube kanti ngizabenza bafelwe, kungasali muntu. Yebo-ke, maye\x + \xt 2 Kho. 17.18; Dute. 31.17; Jer. 6.8; Hos. 5.6.\x* kubo ekusukeni kwami\x + \xt 1 Sam. 28.15,16; Hez. 10.18.\x* kubo!
\v 13 UEfrayimi, njengokubona kwami iTire, uhlanyelwe endaweni yokuhlala; kodwa uEfrayimi uzakhuphela\x + \xt Jobe 27.14; Lilo 2.22,16.; Hos. 13.16; Isa. 65.23.\x* abantwana bakhe kumbulali.
\v 14 Banike, N\nd kosi\nd*! Uzanikani? Banike isizalo esiphunzayo\x + \xt Luka 23.29.\x*\x + \xt Gen. 31.38; Jobe 21.10.\x*, lamabele omileyo\x + \xt Luka 23.29.\x*.
\v 15 Bonke ububi babo buseGiligali\x + \xt Hos. 4.15.\x*, ngoba ngabazonda khona, ngenxa yobubi bezenzo zabo, ngizabaxotsha endlini yami, kangisayikubathanda; zonke iziphathamandla zabo\x + \xt Isa. 1.23.\x* zingabahlamuki\x + \xt Hos. 4.16.\x*.
\v 16 UEfrayimi utshayiwe; impande yabo\x + \xt Hos. 9.16\x*\x + \xt Jobe 18.16.\x* yomile, kabayikuthela isithelo; yebo loba\x + \xt Jobe 27.14; Lilo 2.22,16; Hos. 13.16; Isa. 65.23.\x* bezala, ngizabulala \add izithelo\add* zesizalo sabo ezithandekayo\x + \xt Hos. 9.6.\x*.
\v 17 UNkulunkulu wami uzabala, ngoba kabamlaleli; bazakuba\x + \xt Dute. 28.64,65.\x* ngabazulayo phakathi kwezizwe.